Four people confirmed dead, others sustained injuries in a boat accident in Hartebeespoort Dam, North West on Saturday.One person was burnt to death in the bathroom and three people have drowned, according to reports.When the boat caught fire smaller boats in the area went closer to help, but were overloaded and capsized.Paramedics on scene say it was one of the party boats that caught fire and the cause is still unknown.&#8211;TNA Reporter